commit.message:
fixup sh bustage after r209483

When making pass::execute functions take a function * argument I missed
the sh_treg_combine pass, so fix that here.

gcc/
	* config/sh/sh_treg_combine.c (sh_treg_combine::execute): Take
	function * argument.

From-SVN: r209751
